snippet.title: Rocket League® - Revenge of the Battle-Cars DLC Pack Trailer
snippet.description: We go back to our roots this October with the Revenge of the Battle-Cars DLC Pack! Inspired by Rocket League's predecessor, Supersonic Acrobatic Rocket-Powered Battle-Cars, our next add-on includes two classic vehicles, six unique Decals for each new Battle-Car (12 total), three new Paint Types, two new Wheels, two new Rocket Boosts, four new Toppers, and two new Antennas!
